      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, I think you got the candidates mixed up. I'm working for Vance, so the critique should be against his *opponent*. The current draft sounds like you're attacking Vance. \n\nCan you redo that, but focus the attack on how the opponent's plan will destroy the economy and hurt small businesses? Make it sound like their plan is totally out of touch with real people.",
